26 4-88-1501. Title.
27 This subchapter shall be known and may be cited as the "Poultry
28 Integrators Deceptive Trade Practices and Taxpayer Protection Act".
29
30 4-88-1502. Poultry integrator transparency — Definition.
31 (a) As used in this section, "poultry integrator" means a company that
32 owns poultry throughout the poultry growing process by supplying food,
33 medicine, or other needs for the poultry under a contract with a grower.
34 (b) An owner or operator of a poultry integrator shall not:
35 (1) Fail to disclose a material fact related to the business
36 health of the poultry integrator's business to a grower in contract
